      "writtenOn": "2026-07-21T06:12:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Wouldn\u0027t this be an infinite loop when:\n\n`nextPartRequired \u003d true;` and `CommandInterface::exec()` fails early before reaching `parseResponseMsg`\n\nThere are two cases where CommandInterface:exec() return early:\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/pldm/blob/9fd86d58bd57f01a9b40d6d1f4a88a0c069c002b/pldmtool/pldm_cmd_helper.cpp#L102\n\nhttps://github.com/openbmc/pldm/blob/9fd86d58bd57f01a9b40d6d1f4a88a0c069c002b/pldmtool/pldm_cmd_helper.cpp#L112",
      "revId": "82885751a6c44a5896aaa7b8af2c5560b3c964e7",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "d3b99a1d_40e2dae0",
        "filename": "pldmtool/pldm_fru_cmd.cpp",
        "patchSetId": 5
